  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the wok to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Gather the fillo dough and phyllo pastry, cutting them into 1-inch squares.",
    "In a bowl, mix the feta cheese, Greek yogurt, cucumber, red onion, bell pepper, mushrooms, and garlic.",
    "Add the fajita seasoning and pasta water to the bowl, stirring to combine.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the olive oil and fresh dill.",
    "Dip each fillo square into the olive oil mixture, coating both sides evenly.",
    "Stack the coated fillo squares in a wok, weaving them in a lattice pattern.",
    "Bake the pastry wheel in the preheated wok for 20 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Let the pastry wheel rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving.",
    "Slice the pastry wheel into thin strips, serving with the feta-cheese mixture on the side.",
    "Garnish with additional fresh dill and serve immediately."
  ],
